    <item>
      <title>等待美国生产者价格指数 (PPI) 数据，股市苦苦支撑：市场收尾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者等待美国通胀数据，以寻找有关美联储利率路径的线索，亚洲股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 22:32:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚承诺减免生活成本，同时争取盈余</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/australia-eyes-second-budget-surplus-despite-iron-ore-price-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财长吉姆·查尔默斯表示，澳大利亚将进一步为饱受通货膨胀和高利率困扰的家庭提供生活成本救济，同时敦促实现第二次预算盈余以重建财政缓冲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/australia-eyes-second-budget-surplus-despite-iron-ore-price-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
